Popular Nollywood actress, Regina Daniels, has reacted to reports making the rounds on social media claiming that her billionaire husband, Ned Nwoko is set to marry another wife. The rumour emerged on social media after the wife of the billionaire shared a post on her Instagram story, with a ringed finger and captioned it ‘wifey’. On close inspection, the finger belonged to a lady she tagged @sar8al. However, Regina in a recent post refuted the rumour as she clarified that the lady is her friend, adding that the news that she was Nwoko’s new wife was false. Her post read: “The news about Sara being my husband’s wife is completely false. She is my friend who came visiting!!!”